  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.10">
<l>maṟaiyāya nālvētattu ṇiṉṟa malarccuṭarē</l>
<l>muṟaiyāliv vulakellām paṭaittiṭantuṇ ṭumiḻntaḷantāy</l>
<l>piṟaiyēṟu caṭaiyāṉu nāṉmukaṉu mintiraṉu</l>
<l>miṟaiyāta laṟintētta vīṟṟirutta lituviyappē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O blooming light that stands in the four Vedas that were secret,</l>
<l>you who in turn created, scooped up, swallowed, ejected [and] measured all this world,</l>
<l>while the one with the crescent moon, bull [nd] matted hair, the four-faced one and Indra</l>
<l>praise [know], knowing that you are the lord, [your] sitting in distinction, is this a wonder?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
